---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service - ToolBox"
  description="ToolBox Terms of Service. Understand the terms and conditions when using our services."
  keywords="terms of service,service agreement,ToolBox"
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <a href="/en" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white mb-8 transition-colors">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M10 4L6 8l4 4"/></svg>
      Back to home
    </a>

    <article class="max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: July 5, 2026</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Welcome to ToolBox ("Site"). By accessing or using this Site, you agree to be bound by all terms and conditions of this Agreement. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use this Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Service Description</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          ToolBox is a collection of online tools providing various utilities including a Steam Card Generator. All tools are free to use with no registration required. We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate any tool at any time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Usage Guidelines</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">When using this Site, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful or unauthorized purpose</li>
          <li>Attempt unauthorized access to our servers or systems</li>
          <li>Use automated tools (such as crawlers or bots) to extensively access the Site</li>
          <li>Distribute malware, viruses, or other harmful code</li>
          <li>Infringe on the intellectual property rights or legitimate interests of others</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          The content, design, code, and trademarks of this Site are protected by intellectual property laws. No copying, distribution, or creation of derivative works is allowed without written permission. Third-party trademarks and brands used on this Site belong to their respective owners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          This Site is provided "as is" without any express or implied warranties. We do not guarantee that the tools will be uninterrupted or error-free. We are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of this Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          This Site may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for convenience only. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of third-party websites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Agreement Modifications</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Modified terms will be posted on this page with a new effective date. Continued use of the Site constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us via GitHub Issues.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
